	measure 'Revenue YoY Growth %' = ```
			
			VAR CurrentYearRevenue = [Total Revenue]
			VAR PreviousYearRevenue = 
			    CALCULATE(
			        [Total Revenue], 
			        FiscalCalendar[Fiscal Year] = MAX(FiscalCalendar[Fiscal Year]) - 1
			    )
			RETURN
			    DIVIDE(
			        CurrentYearRevenue - PreviousYearRevenue, 
			        PreviousYearRevenue, 
			        0
			    )
			```
		lineageTag: a2a9b6cf-641f-4a61-8983-c0721c51b318

